<li><a href="/wiki/Louis_Bohne" title="Louis Bohne">Louis Bohne</a> - Famous sales agent for Veuve Cliquot in the 19th century</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Coteaux_Champenois_AOC" title="Coteaux Champenois AOC">Coteaux Champenois AOC</a> - Term used for non-sparkling (still) wines produced in the same area.12e</li>
