<li id="cite_note-32"><b><a href="#cite_ref-32" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFRoberts_C.2C_Robinson_SP2007">Roberts C, Robinson SP (2007). "Alcohol concentration and carbonation of drinks: The effect on blood alcohol levels". <i>J Forensic Legal Med</i> <b>14</b>: 398–405. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.jflm.2006.12.010" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.jflm.2006.12.010" rel="nofollow">10.1016/j.jflm.2006.12.010</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Alcohol+concentration+and+carbonation+of+drinks%3A+The+effect+on+blood+alcohol+levels&amp;rft.jtitle=J+Forensic+Legal+Med&amp;rft.aulast=Roberts+C%2C+Robinson+SP&amp;rft.au=Roberts+C%2C+Robinson+SP&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.volume=14&amp;rft.pages=398%26ndash%3B405&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1016%2Fj.jflm.2006.12.010&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Champagne_(wine)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
